{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Rnq2QuFLkq9vTbXwZcAvoK","type":"tool_result","content":"# Plage de Saint-Jorioz Information\n\n**Commune:** Saint-Jorioz\n\n**Entrance Fee:** The beach has variable pricing. According to the listing: \"Placený vstup v červenci a srpnu (2,60 €), zbytek roku zdarma\" — paid entry during July and August at €2.60, free admission the rest of the year.\n\n**Detail Page Link:** https://loisirs74.fr/cs/plage-de-saint-jorioz\n\n**Additional Details:** This is described as a large natural sandy beach on Lac d'Annecy with views of Dents de Lanfon, featuring a Blue Flag designation."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa11e8a2-00bc-490d-9dcb-0538062593e4","uuid":"687f5fb2-bea4-4b98-83a1-7c8473f599ea","timestamp":"2026-07-05T22:50:11.963Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":160440,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Plage de Saint-Jorioz Information\n\n**Commune:** Saint-Jorioz\n\n**Entrance Fee:** The beach has variable pricing. According to the listing: \"Placený vstup v červenci a srpnu (2,60 €), zbytek roku zdarma\" — paid entry during July and August at €2.60, free admission the rest of the year.\n\n**Detail Page Link:** https://loisirs74.fr/cs/plage-de-saint-jorioz\n\n**Additional Details:** This is described as a large natural sandy beach on Lac d'Annecy with views of Dents de Lanfon, featuring a Blue Flag designation.","durationMs":3507,"url":"https://loisirs74.fr/cs/"}}
